<div class="page-header">
  <h1>Buttons <small>icons</small></h1>
</div>

<p>
  Along with the different sizes, you can also add a number of different types of Icons to your buttons, a few of which are show in the following example:
</p>

<div class="spacedDiv"><a href="#" class="btn"><i class="icon-home"></i> Home</a></div>
<div class="spacedDiv"><a href="#" class="btn btn-primary"><i class="icon-print"></i> Print</a></div>
<div class="spacedDiv"><a href="#" class="btn btn-info"><i class="icon-info-sign"></i> Get Information</a></div>
<div class="spacedDiv"><a href="#" class="btn btn-success"><i class="icon-ok-circle"></i> Everything Worked</a></div>
<div class="spacedDiv"><a href="#" class="btn btn-warning"><i class="icon-question-sign"></i> Are you sure</a></div>
<div class="spacedDiv"><a href="#" class="btn btn-danger"><i class="icon-remove-circle"></i> Delete Item</a></div>
<div class="spacedDiv"><a href="#" class="btn btn-inverse"><i class="icon-play"></i> Play</a></div>
<div class="spacedDiv"><a href="#" class="btn btn-link"><i class="icon-tasks"></i> List Tasks</a></div>

<pre>
  &lt;div class="spacedDiv"&gt;&lt;a href="#" class="btn"&gt;&lt;i class="icon-home"&gt;&lt;/i&gt; Home&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class="spacedDiv"&gt;&lt;a href="#" class="btn btn-primary"&gt;&lt;i class="icon-print"&gt;&lt;/i&gt; Print&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class="spacedDiv"&gt;&lt;a href="#" class="btn btn-info"&gt;&lt;i class="icon-info-sign"&gt;&lt;/i&gt; Get Information&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class="spacedDiv"&gt;&lt;a href="#" class="btn btn-success"&gt;&lt;i class="icon-ok-circle"&gt;&lt;/i&gt; Everything Worked&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class="spacedDiv"&gt;&lt;a href="#" class="btn btn-warning"&gt;&lt;i class="icon-question-sign"&gt;&lt;/i&gt; Are you sure&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
